  "prompt": "Can a Guitar Hero guitar be used in Rock Band?",
  "response": "In general, a Guitar Hero guitar can be used with some Rock Band games, but compatibility can vary depending on the specific models and platforms. For example, the earlier Guitar Hero controllers typically work with the PlayStation 2 and PS3 versions of Rock Band, while newer models may not be as compatible.\n\nFor Xbox systems, compatibility is more limited, and many players find that Guitar Hero instruments do not work with Rock Band titles. It's important to check for specific compatibility information related to your game console and the version of Rock Band you're playing.\n\nIf you're looking to use a Guitar Hero guitar for Rock Band, it's recommended to verify compatibility online or through community forums specific to your console and games.",
